gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

I am happy in good company, I'll tell you what happens after that; 
Many names of Maharaj are, who remains in the forest at night.

I understand the couplet as:

Very old time I know, old time,
Fattens mouth big calamity; 
Sharp are horns of goat, bird;
Human flesh has come to fill in it.
